				h1.articleheading what is DEADEYE's skill?
				p.articletext Expertly trained with long-range and short-range weapons, DEADEYE has superb combat reflexes and pinpoint accuracy. An experienced war veteran, DEADEYE is not above using surveillance devices and explosives to hunt her targets. DEADEYE's skill AIM represents her ability to deal extra damage by hitting her opponent right where it counts.

				.row.articleskillrow
					.col-md-12.text-center.articleskillpanel
						img(src="http://res.cloudinary.com/jhi5/image/upload/e_auto_contrast,q_54:420,r_25/v1498676135/aim.jpg")
						h4.articleskilltext Cards in your deck give you Aim points. Whenever your Actions or Feats deal damage, add your Aim to that damage. At the end of each turn, reset your Aim to 0.

				p.articletext So how does Aim work? Your Aim score is represented by a number that begins each turn at 0. Increasing your Aim score provides your Actions and Feats with a temporary damage boost. DEADEYE players can take advantage of this powerful ability by waiting for a big Aim bonus! 

				p.articeltext Let's look at an example...

